title: Day 1233
content:
# Day 1233

![I hope everyone gets to experience this one day](https://miro.medium.com/1*etXvReBFRdJRvPQ8yNNj_A.png)

There is one thing you can't make with a 3D printer. And that would be children.

Of course you should still get a 3D printer. When you have one you can create anything you can dream up. Except a child of course. But still 3D printers are amazing. Incredible for prototyping.

So PSA - Get a 3D printer and have kids. Life is better with them.

Both 3D printers and kids of course.

8/6/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
